      {
        "block_label": "text",
        "block_content": "We employed GSA $ _{1} $ and GSA $ _{2} $ on CIFAR-10, ImageNet, and MS COCO to further conduct layer-wise reduction as mentioned in Section 3.2, aiming to reduce computational time and resource consumption. The experimental results are presented in Figure 9.",
